The Karth House seems to be an old hotel that's been condemned for years. Detective Durkin asked us to meet him here. As for why, he didn't say.[[So far, he's a no show.

Detective Durkin

Detective Durkin helped us out with a case earlier this year. He doesn't know who we are, but he knows enough not to ask questions.[[He occasionally asks us to consult for him.

Cast and Crew

Downloaded a file that contains a list of all the cast and crew members for every performance that the Gotham Collective put on.

The ghost on the third floor of the Karth House is named Mary.

Gotham Collective

We found a photograph of the ghost on a memory stick. The photo was an actress's headshot, and the words "Gotham Collective" were written on it. A theater company, most likely.

The River Wall

A theater performance put together by the Gotham Collective. Mary was a cast member.

Drug raid

A newspaper article described a drug raid at a condemned building in Chelsea. Several drug addicts were found and an unidentified woman was found dead.

Murdered man

We saw a man murdered last night, and his ghost was torn apart right in front of us.[[No mention of the murder in the news. Perhaps the police know something?

Grace

The murdered man last night said the name "Grace", and that she wasn't safe.

Lia

In a prayer written by George, he hoped to save himself and somebody named Lia.

Inside Lia Pierro's house, we found the spirit of a little girl named Kendra Haskins.

Abacus

Kendra's father works at a place called "The Abacus". He is apparently the boss there.

Emil Haskins

Emil is Kendra's father, and Lia's ex-husband. He lives in the East Village in a building called the "Exeter House."[[He seems genuinely distraught over what's happened.

Trollgate

Kendra was a fan of an online game called "Trollgate."

Michael's #

A man named Michael called George Ostin the night he was killed.[[He called from the number 212-555-3412.

Gabriel Ullman

Father Gabriel Ullman is a priest at Grace Church.

Grace Group

When I spoke to Lia, she said that she was part of a self-help group that met in the basement of Grace Church. She called it the "Grace Group."

Michael

George received several emails from someone named Michael.[[Whoever this Michael is, he appears to know a LOT about what's going on.

Jeffrey Dutta

George Ostin received an email from someone named Michael.[[In the email, Michael wrote that he saw Jeffrey's soul being ripped apart.

George Ostin received an email from someone named Michael.[[In the email, Michael wrote about someone named Peter who died recently. Michael is worried that Peter might have encountered "the same fate" as the others.

Jeffrey, Peter, and Heather

George Ostin received an email from someone named Michael. In the email, Michael asked if George knew where Heather was. There was no answer.

Michael Cooper told us that a Japanese man named Benjiro ran the Grace Group meetings.

Roof ghost

We found the ghost of a woman on the roof deck outside of George's apartment. She seems to live - or rather, LIVED - in the apartment next door.

Heather's ghost asked Joey if "Ray sent him."

Jim Peebles

Jim is a producer at Channel 11. He works on the show that Tanya Corsey used to host.

Client list

I have a list of all of Ray's clients.[[There are... quite a lot of them.

Peter's number

Peter Fielding's ghost gave us his phone number. It's 646-555-0425, for all the good it will do us.

Connor Fielding

Peter and Maggie's father is dead and buried in Greenwood Cemetery. He died over twenty years ago on March 18th, 1993. Maggie doesn't want to talk about him.

Maggie Fielding

Maggie is Peter Fielding's sister. She is living in Peter's apartment.

Case #

The probation ID number for the woman living in Peter's apartment.

Karth File

The police case notes on the Karth House arrests.

