Careless?

Strands of red hair in an upstairs room. Fingerprints on a piece of glass.

Pieces of evidence that only a select few know about. Evidence that has been locked away and hidden. Unless they are uncovered. 

Do we understand each other?

You mean work for the police? I already do.

Right now you are off the books. An embarrassment to one police detective who denies working with you. I want to change that.  

