You are official now. Congratulations.

You need information? We're obliged to give it to you. 

No runarounds. No obstruction.  Not anymore.

What brought this on? Why now?

Desperate times, The dead are under attack, and who is better qualified to help them but you?

My colleagues can do much, but speaking to the dead is not one of them.

Now, I suggest you go home and get some sleep. I believe you have work to do.

